# RNA-seq Intro Training (Wet-lab Friendly)

This training module introduces basic R and RNA-seq data handling using a small GEO dataset (GSE155432). 
Itâ€™s intended for wet-lab scientists learning how to explore and visualize RNA-seq count data.

